唔好爭住屌一毛、恥笑一毛，亦唔好跟住留「唔好再覆」，否則等同推po。2）俾正負評前睇埋最後一頁，唔好俾第一頁帶風向。3）新聞po睇日期先覆，小心一毛伎倆：有人推舊po、出引戰po、傳聞po。最後，721去遊行！</code>"},{"pid":"4c6d6cad38a7ddaee09df596c85e8ad7cc455c67","tid":1332010,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T07:48:14.000Z","msg":"721 維園見<br />\n<br />\n【721整合】721整合Post！全部推哂上熱門！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1329038\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1329038</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"473dc979346761808d14c832ec41c5dda2938264","tid":1332010,"uid":156791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T07:48:33.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"e4107efc6e50688b62355b2d6fa873f701adfd79","tid":1332010,"uid":22116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T07:50:35.000Z","msg":"今日文宣720改721<br />\n聽日文宣721大遊行 五大訴求 真普選 獨立調查黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}